data.description: Welcome home to 2019 Chesapeake Bay, this home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms along with a 3 car garage. Walking into the open concept living space there is a wood-burning fireplace and tray ceilings. This home features a split floor-plan with the primary bedroom and ensuite bathroom and one bedroom and half-bath on one side of the home.  There is another 2 bedrooms and 1 bath on the other side of the property.  In the kitchen there is ample counter and cabinet space and a large pantry. Off of the kitchen is the separate laundry room and drop zone.  This home is located within walking distance to Andrews Elementary and the Portland Municipal Park.
